PrintSetupCustomDiagramRepeat Property

Requires: Base Development System

Class: Application Properties (ActiveX)

Specifies whether to print visible subdiagrams of each Case, Event, and Stacked Sequence structure in sequence with the non-visible subdiagrams when using the custom format with one of the print documentation VI methods. If you print the visible frames in sequence, those frames will print twice.

Syntax

object.PrintSetupCustomDiagramRepeat

Data Type

Boolean
